Kiharu MP Irungu Kang ata (pictured) has an interest in the Senate seat. He is rumoured to have held meetings with local leaders and sought their advice. The 35-year-old, first-term MP served as a civic leader from 2002 to 2007. Kang ata said he will make a major announcement soon . He shrugged off the question about his candidacy, telling journalists to read my lips .